71,"uid":128261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T01:54:35.000Z","msg":"睇條撚樣個髮型同樣都覺得似公安或者國安啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記者通常斯文啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e69c67926548379e7a7d4354561aec067af7c245","tid":1479371,"uid":265951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T01:55:09.000Z","msg":"pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5087169d85bf4ce49068d650fd15997167ed5780","tid":1479371,"uid":268094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T01:55:30.000Z","msg":"知啦<br />\n環球時報<br />\n屌 紅媒<br />\n係藍絲on99<br />\n幾廿年中共都係咁做野"},{"pid":"dd68880c5a84ed1c4663bf533787f2443c7627a9","tid":1479371,"uid":187232,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T02:01:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190815/s00001/1565881331334/警元朗檢7汽油彈-拘三人包括兩內地男\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190815%2Fs00001%2F1565881331334%2F%E8%AD%A6%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E6%AA%A27%E6%B1%BD%E6%B2%B9%E5%BD%88-%E6%8B%98%E4%B8%89%E4%BA%BA%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E5%85%A9%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%B7&d=u3dPEc69Okhs1BcqxCk75ZmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=9c2e59f3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190815%2Fs00001%2F1565881331334%2F%E8%AD%A6%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E6%AA%A27%E6%B1%BD%E6%B2%B9%E5%BD%88-%E6%8B%98%E4%B8%89%E4%BA%BA%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E5%85%A9%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%B7&h=a84c5bfb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190815/s00001/1565881331334/警元朗檢7汽油彈-拘三人包括兩內地男</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190816/20750204\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190816%2F20750204&d=u3dPEc69Okhs1BcqxCk75ZmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=1f82c3ab\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190816%2F20750204&h=c9f682e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190816/20750204</a><br />\n<br />\n車藏汽油彈　兩內地男被捕<br />\n2019-08-16<br />\n頭條<br />\n <br />\n元朗警署<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】警方昨凌晨在元朗路邊截查一輛可疑私家車，站在車旁的三名男子見狀逃跑但被擒獲，當中包括兩名內地男子。其間車上掉出一個紙箱，警員在箱內撿獲七個汽油彈，另一疑人則駕車逃去。警方正調查案件是否與近期連串示威活動中，警方被投擲汽油彈的事件有關。<br />\n<br />\n被捕三人包括兩名同姓李的男子（35歲及26歲），他們均為內地人；另一人則姓程（61歲），為本地人。三人涉嫌藏有工具可作非法用途被捕。至於另一駕駛私家車的男子仍然在逃，警方正追緝該司機及私家車歸案。<br />\n<br />\n司機仍在逃<br />\n<br />\n現場是元朗青山公路屏山段往天水圍方向，昨凌晨1時許，警員巡邏時發現一輛形迹可疑的私家車停泊在上址，遂上前截查。涉案三名被捕男子當時站在車旁，他們見有警員隨即拔足向元朗市方向逃走，但終被警員擒獲。私家車司機則駕駛私家車往屯門方向逃去，其間車上掉出一個紙箱，警員發現紙箱內有七個汽油彈。事件中35歲姓李內地男子逃走時受傷，其後由救護員送院治療，案件交由元朗警區刑事調查隊跟進。<br />\n<br />\n■記者黎國剛"},{"pid":"d24d59588f350b849f031e365ecd5e4bb8aa8044","tid":1479371,"uid":226956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T02:02:36.000Z","msg":"我都話，要相信侵侵，唔會唔搞！"},{"pid":"f7c1595b5d8ac737d0967b15da3e84635085a6fb","tid":1479371,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T02:05:09.000Z","msg":"即改新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n機場英雄變嫖客 笑到仆街XDDDDDDD<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1479295\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1479295</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6add7f512fd87d7437bfd398744bc2560952bbe9","tid":1479371,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T02:06:04.000Z","msg":"叫到天安門廣場，那個海報我也看了，這個現在小粉紅、五毛高漲情緒嘛，你一說上街他們就不敢說話。那個就是他們軟肋嘛。太搞笑了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47545af537ba7f9be86be4bfa7e438dba430